siteMetadata.defaultTitle: Austin, Texas Architecture - Faye + Walker Architects
siteMetadata.defaultDescription: Faye + Walker is an Austin based multidisciplinary firm working primarily in the medium of Architecture. Our vision is to facilitate thoughtful dialog about space, function and individuality.
siteMetadata.headline: We contribute to the emotional capital of our community through considerate manipulations of the built environment.
siteMetadata.author: Sean Guess
